text:
India in away chases this year:

Cape Town - Target 208 - LOST
Centurion - Target 287 - LOST
Edgbaston - Target 194 - LOST
Southampton - Target 245 - LOST
The Oval - Target 464 - LOST

Perth - Target 287 - lost

#AusvInd #away #test #chasing

6th time in 2018 that India has lost a Test match while chasing a target.

No other team has lost more than four Tests in a calendar year while chasing a target.
#AUSvIND #test #chasing
